title: Wheat Crop for France
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1815-1919 (2)--Original Data, 1919-1938. Original Data Given In Quintals, Converted To Bushels By Using The Equivalent--One Quintal=3.67437 Bushels. Source: Statistique Agricole Annuelle, 1929, Pp. 180-184.
